Class ContactList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.providenceuniversal.gim.ContactList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServerMessage, Serializable

    public class ContactList
extends Object
implements ServerMessage
    The ContactList class stores a list of all the users of G-Instant Messenger, and indicates their activity status. It is one of the types of ServerMessage.
